des: Your daily espresso-strength shot of mental caffeine. This flash briefing will rev your confidence and your courage for the day. Trish Blackwell, world renown confidence coach gives you a daily pep talk for your mindset. These flash briefings will help you train your thoughts - and subsequently, when you train your thoughts, you will change your thoughts - and when you change your thoughts, you change your life. The quality of your thinking determines the quality of your life. A Shot of Confidence is the daily confidence boost everyone needs. Get more info on Trish and more free confidence resources at www.trishblackwell.com or www.collegeofconfidence.com
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
